  <p class="gd-lede">A heliski trip is one of the most photogenic things you will ever do, and with a little planning you can bring the whole adventure home in pictures and video. Here is how to capture it well, and safely, before you explore <a href="/packages">the packages</a> and <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
